Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.60,Utama,Eric,0,0,0,,Kebetulan saja dia sedang tidak ingin makanan manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.00,Utama,Liz,0,0,0,,Eric ....
