Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.52,Utama,Liz,0,0,0,,Jika aku berusaha lebih keras lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.67,Utama,Liz,0,0,0,,kuyakin Duke akan kembali tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.69,Utama,Liz,0,0,0,,Aku percaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.56,Utama,Albert,0,0,0,,Ucapanmu pasti tidak akan salah, Liz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.34,Utama,Eric,0,0,0,,Iya!
